cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_PORT_FOR_S1U to 99999 (out of valid port range 1-65535 but invalid for S1-U) will cause S1-U interface connection failures and GTP tunnel establishment errors.

du.explanation_en: Setting dl_absoluteFrequencyPointA equal to absoluteFrequencySSB (641280) causes frequency misalignment, leading to incorrect downlink carrier configuration and potential SSB synchronization faults.
